abstract: 'A streaming log anomaly detector that scores each log line (TF-IDF + IsolationForest),
  targets a 1% false-positive rate via Sliding Conformal calibration, and adapts to distribution
  drift with ADWIN-triggered recalibration. The project emphasizes strict, auditable reproducibility:
  UTF-8/LF policy, byte-exact protected JSONs, canonical data/HASHES.txt, 24-column experiments/summary.csv,
  and CI-pinned environments.'
